title: Windkracht 10 Season 2 Dutch
description:
Windkracht 10, Seizoen 2

This drama series is about a small helicopter unit of the Belgian Air Force based at Koksijde, on the North Sea coast. This unit specializes in search and rescue operations at sea. The interactions of the various staff (crew, maintenance, command, logistics, communications, administration...) on the base and some of their personal lives, also provide various story lines.


Language: Vlaams/Dutch
